Package: terminal-studio
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libxkbcommon0, libwayland-client0, libx11-6, libxcb1, libvulkan1 | libegl1
Maintainer: Deepak Jha <deepakjha.dpk@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/dpkay-io/terminal-studio
Description: GPU-accelerated terminal multiplexer
 Terminal Studio is a GPU-accelerated terminal multiplexer built with
 Rust and egui/wgpu. Features multi-pane terminals, workspaces, file
 browser, git integration, and markdown preview.
